What kind of music is that?

801
01:04:40,820 --> 01:04:42,036
What happened to swing?

802
01:04:42,196 --> 01:04:43,214
Benny Goodman?

803
01:04:43,739 --> 01:04:45,027
You're like a time traveler man.

804
01:04:45,662 --> 01:04:47,305
