Let's get off this island.

857
01:08:37,159 --> 01:08:38,160
Not yet!

858
01:08:38,446 --> 01:08:40,075
- Behind the lines.
- Yes.

859
01:08:40,927 --> 01:08:42,015
Bind it up, Let's go!

860
01:08:43,217 --> 01:08:44,419
Keep going!

861
01:08:49,122 --> 01:08:51,123
Third time's the charm.
Here we go.

862
01:08:52,377 --> 01:08:54,191
let's go. let's go.

863
01:08:54,490 --> 01:08:56,026
Come on.

864
01:08:57,738 --> 01:08:58,740
Yes.

865
01:09:02,757 --> 01:09:04,486
Yes!

866
01:09:30,088 --> 01:09:31,809
I guess this is good bye.

867
01:09:33,745 --> 01:09:34,819
Thank you.

868
01:09:43,794 --> 01:09:46,283
If you're ever in Chicago,
look me up, I guess.

869
01:11:14,412 --> 01:11:16,305
Yeah, no. Let me, let me help.

870
01:11:17,828 --> 01:11:19,321
A man has gotta do what...

871
01:11:19,657 --> 01:11:20,658
Are you okay?

872
01:11:20,683 --> 01:11:21,800
I'm Okay, I'm okay.

873
01:11:22,250 --> 01:11:23,291
Allow me.

874
01:11:24,364 --> 01:11:26,030
You should see me in the library.

875
01:11:28,921 --> 01:11:30,459
I got a wife.

876
01:11:30,769 --> 01:11:31,799
Had a wife.

877
01:11:31,958 --> 01:11:33,329
Have a wife?

878
01:11:34,672 --> 01:11:36,043
I guess I don't know.

879
01:11:37,730 --> 01:11:39,423
Got hitched right before I deplyed.

880
01:11:40,003 --> 01:11:42,557
Got a telegram from her the day
