881
01:11:42,582 --> 01:11:44,223
She said we just had our baby boy.

882
01:11:44,773 --> 01:11:45,774
I have a son out there.

883
01:11:46,777 --> 01:11:48,535
Grown man I've never met

884
01:11:48,560 --> 01:11:50,205
Yeah, she definitely
thinks you're dead man.

885
01:11:50,590 --> 01:11:51,591
Hey!

886
01:11:52,947 --> 01:11:53,948
I'm just saying

887
