900
01:12:23,331 --> 01:12:25,686
We clean up, there is lika a crazy
Santa Clause, a time traveler.

901
01:12:25,711 --> 01:12:27,551
A guy from World War II. You'll meet him.

902
01:12:27,577 --> 01:12:28,658
What kind of boat?

903
01:12:28,954 --> 01:12:30,900
It is more like a plane than a boat really.

904
01:12:30,925 --> 01:12:31,992
And it's called a float.

905
01:12:32,646 --> 01:12:33,376
Quantepo.

906
01:12:33,400 --> 01:12:34,968
We need that location Slivko.

907
01:12:34,993 --> 01:12:36,662
Send up a flare so we could find you..

908
01:12:38,254 --> 01:12:39,656
Roger that, Fox Five.

909
01:12:39,752 --> 01:12:41,107
Fire in the hole!

910
01:12:46,413 --> 01:12:47,814
There!

911
01:12:47,952 --> 01:12:49,842
Yes!

912
01:12:49,867 --> 01:12:52,466
I repeat, we have a visual.
2 clicks to our north.

913
01:12:52,491 --> 01:12:54,828
Roger that, Fox Five. Fox One, out.

914
01:12:56,242 --> 01:12:58,465
rendezvous point, in one hour.

915
01:12:58,824 --> 01:12:59,583
Mount up!

916
01:12:59,608 --> 01:13:01,169
Can we fit everybody?

917
